<item>
            <title>[LU-15403] improve a sanity 901 a bit.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15403</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Current test implementation have a two bugs.&lt;br/&gt;
1) client mgc llogs processing is async to mount, so we can start a lock check before all locks processed, it caused a false alarm.&lt;br/&gt;
2) Server locks counting is unsafe, as it include an other server locks. so Any client reconnect may cause a false alarm.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let&apos;s fix it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
